Is there are way to summarise CVS changes as you do for Releases of Jira issues. For example a part of our release management process is to assign Jira's to a release, which we run release notes from.

Is there a way of providing CVS details as a summary report for the Jira issues assigned to the release, as opposed to have to check the version of each Jira?

